# Git Rules

Never push directly to main. Main is protected.
Always work on a feature branch.
Branch naming: feature/D-XXX-short-description

Never commit:
- .env files
- __pycache__/
- *.pyc
- Any file containing secrets or API keys

Every PR must reference a D-number from DECISIONS.md.
Never auto-merge. Always wait for CI to pass.
